{{if .WithConfig}}
## Configuration

Default config: `./configs/config.toml`

| Key | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `env` | `development` | Runtime environment (`development` \| `production`) |
| `log-level` | `info` | Log level (`debug` \| `info` \| `warn` \| `error`) |
| `hello.greeting` | `Hello` | Greeting string |
| `hello.default-name` | `World` | Default name for the hello command |

Environment-specific overlay: create `configs/config_<env>.toml` and set `APP_ENV=<env>`.
Override path at runtime: `{{.Name}} --config /path/to/config.toml`.
{{end}}
## Development

{{if eq .Toolchain "make"}}
| Command | Description |
|---|---|
| `make build` | Build binary to `./bin/{{.Name}}` |
| `make test` | Run tests |
| `make test/cover` | Run tests with coverage |
| `make lint` | Run golangci-lint |
| `make install` | Install to `GOPATH/bin` |
| `make clean` | Remove `./bin/` |
{{else}}
| Command | Description |
|---|---|
| `mise run build` | Build binary to `./bin/{{.Name}}` |
| `mise run test` | Run tests |
| `mise run test:cover` | Run tests with coverage |
| `mise run lint` | Run golangci-lint |
| `mise run install` | Install to `GOPATH/bin` |
| `mise run clean` | Remove `./bin/` |
{{end}}
